I was trained in a research-based protocol to conduct interviews of children to gather information when there are allegations of child abuse. MS. MENNINGER: Objection, your Honor. 702. MS. COMEY: I have no intention of eliciting -- MS. MENNINGER: -- and no disclosure and -- THE COURT: I understand, Ms. Menninger. Let me hear from you at the side, please.
